figgy.title: BrowseEverything uploads fail to enqueue for Google Drive intermittently

comments.body: This behavior seems to be local to the `ChangeSetPersister`, as I am locally able to select files and have them passed into https://github.com/pulibrary/figgy/blob/master/app/jobs/browse_everything_ingest_job.rb#L83
https://github.com/pulibrary/figgy/blob/master/app/services/file_appender.rb#L60 is filtering `PendingUpload` objects.
https://github.com/pulibrary/figgy/blob/master/app/services/file_appender.rb#L68 is also failing with a `Typhoeus` error.

https://figgy-staging.princeton.edu/catalog/3b881b85-ee7b-482e-a09a-c7ccb8509624 now works (as tested in the staging environment). I would please prefer to test this for a few more uploads before submitting a PR.
